cmd-showalert-desc = Shows an alert for a player.
cmd-showalert-help = Usage: showalert <alertType> <severity> [user]
                     alertType: Type of alert that will be given.
                     severity: An integer representing severity. -1 indicates no severity.
                     user: ID or name of a user to target. If one is not passed, the current player is used.
cmd-showalert-unrecognized = {$alert} is not recognized as an alert type.
cmd-showalert-invalid-severity = {$severity} is not a valid severity level.
